<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">2月22日上午，党委书记、督导专员江延湖主持召开学校2024年春季“开学第一课”暨安全教育周专题工作会。执行校长范红铭，副校长徐国荣、高建国等校领导出席会议并作了讲话，党政办、宣传部、督导办、教务处、学工处、保卫处、招就处、团委、马克思主义学院等部门负责人参加会议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-22%2019%3A21%3A03%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8719.png?Expires=2023960863&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=UQnU7o8KOEGIzS766B2MyZ68bCA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="387" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">会议传达了省教育厅《关于开展</span>&nbsp;2024 年春季“开学第一课”暨安全教育周活动的通知》、省委教育工委宣传部《关于开展好2024年春季“开学第一课”系列教育活动的工作提示》等有关文件精神。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">会议从组织上好校领导</span>“开学第一课”、上好“思政课”、开展好“主题班会”、上好“安全教育课”、上好“心理健康教育课”、上好“劳动教育课”、上好“学业指导课”、上好“就业指导课”、开展系列“实践教育活动”、开展系列“校园文体活动”共十个方面作了工作布置。各有关职能部门进一步细化工作内容，将相应的措施举措落到实处，形成长效机制。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">会议要求以</span>“开学第一课”为重点，利用春季学期开学前后段时间，全覆盖、立体化开展系列教育引导活动，开好讲活“第一课”，推动“时代新人铸魂工程”落实落细落小，努力构建育人大格局大生态。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">会议还要求组织全体辅导员等提前观看安全教育片，并做好授课准备和召开主题教育班会等，要重点围绕消防安全、心理健康教育、交通安全、食品安全、校舍安全和防踩踏、防欺凌、防诈骗、防溺水等方面加强安全教育，帮助广大学生树立正确的安全观念。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">会议强调了要深入贯彻习近平总书记关于安全生产重要指示精神，深刻汲取新余</span>“1·24”特大火灾事故教训，着力提高学生安全防范意识，增强师生自我防护能力，筑牢安全稳定防线，防范各类安全事故。根据学校实际，组织全体师生开展一次以消防逃生为主的应急演练，切实增强师生的避险逃生和自救互救能力。今后，学校定期或不定期地组织师生开展演练活动，提高安全教育的实效性，做到教育与演练相结合、动脑与动手相结合、意识培养与习惯养成相结合，做到教育在前，演练在前，及时总结，不断提高。</span></p><p><br/></p>